top-albums-fusionnes/?ye=2013 |archive-date=14 February 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| 29\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| German Albums (Offizielle Top 100)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/album-jahr/for-date-2013 |title=Top 100 Album-Jahrescharts \u2013 2013 |language=German |publisher=Offizielle Deutsche Charts. GfK Entertainment |accessdate=28 February 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519073341/https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/album-jahr/for-date-2013 |archive-date=19 May 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| 53\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Hungarian Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/archivum/eves-osszesitett-listak/album_chart/2013 |title=\u00d6sszes\u00edtett album- \u00e9s v\u00e1logat\u00e1slemez-lista \u2013 chart-poz\u00edci\u00f3 alapj\u00e1n \u2013 2013 |language=Hungarian |publisher=MAHASZ |accessdate=8 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108180601/http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/archivum/eves-osszesitett-listak/album_chart/2013 |archive-date=8 January 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|75\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Italian Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fimi.it/up/files/pdfddm/Classifiche_Annuali_2013.zip |title=Classifica annuale 2013 \u2013 Top 100 Album Combined |language=Italian |publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]] |accessdate=8 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107154658/http://www.fimi.it/up/files/pdfddm/Classifiche_Annuali_2013.zip |archive-date=7 January 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|38\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|New Zealand Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2348 |title=Top Selling Albums of 2013 |publisher=Recorded Music NZ |accessdate=31 December 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131226221503/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2348 |archivedate=26 December 2013 }}</ref>\n|42\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Spanish Albums Chart<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.promusicae.es/estaticos/view/21-listas-anuales|title=Tops 2013 PROMUSICAE Charts|accessdate=28 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220214549/http://www.promusicae.es/estaticos/view/21-listas-anuales/|archive-date=20 February 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 33\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Swedish Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitlistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=83&dfom=20130001 |title=\u00c5rslista Album \u2013 \u00c5r 2013 |language=Swedish |publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]. [[Swedish Recording Industry Association]] |accessdate=2 March 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012232732/http://www.hitlistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=83&dfom=20130001 |archivedate=12 October 2014 }}</ref>\n|17\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Swiss Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=http://swisscharts.com/year.asp?key=2013 |title=Swiss Year-End Charts 2013 |publisher=swisscharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=2 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125135012/http://swisscharts.com/year.asp?key=2013 |archive-date=25 January 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|39\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|UK Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |last=Lane |first=Daniel |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-artist-albums-of-2013-2708/ |title=The Official Top 40 Biggest Artist Albums Of 2013 |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=1 January 2014 |accessdate=1 January 2014 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6OyqE794u?url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-artist-albums-of-2013-2708/ |archive-date=20 April 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|26\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US ''Billboard'' 200<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2013/the-billboard-200?page=16 |title=Billboard 200 Albums: 2013 Year-End Charts |work=Billboard |accessdate=16 December 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705183821/http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2013/the-billboard-200?page=16 |archi